2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a new network architecture that uses residual connections and auxiliary information from a FER network. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with the development of an intelligent system for facial expression analysis. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with the analysis of facial expressions in images and videos. 
5. cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with the analysis of facial expressions, which is an important aspect of human-computer interaction.
